<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading" lang="en"><span dir="auto">Barnacle goose</span></h1>
<div id="bodyContent" class="mw-body-content">
<div id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</div>
<div id="contentSub">  (Redirected from <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Branta_leucopsis&amp;redirect=no" title="Branta leucopsis">Branta leucopsis</a>)</div>
<div id="jump-to-nav" class="mw-jump">
Jump to: <a href="Branta_leucopsis#mw-navigation">navigation</a>, <a href="Branta_leucopsis#p-search">search</a>
</div>
<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="hatnote">Not to be confused with <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Goose_barnacle" title="Goose barnacle">Goose barnacle</a>.</div>
